{"tid":2321881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港式分居｜26歲年輕夫妻拒租樓 為儲首期抽居屋分居年半 月花$2,000租酒店staycation二人世界","createTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T01:23:38.000Z","uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd463691e8a70071a608c78a689e29dddba67cb","tid":2321881,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:16.000Z","msg":"26歲的張家駿（Jarvis）和胡芷瓊（Elly）拍拖兩年半，去年6月結婚。為了儲首期，他們繼續留在各自的家居住，每逢周末才會到酒店住一晚，享受二人世界。在寸金尺土、樓價貴得誇張的香港，就算暫時未能置業同居，仍希望享受非一般的「港式浪漫」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201211/EQ2BGJLIPFAKJMSQA7DVHP6HMQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_AS.AppleDaily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201211%2FEQ2BGJLIPFAKJMSQA7DVHP6HMQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_AS.AppleDaily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=5b0d0564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201211%2FEQ2BGJLIPFAKJMSQA7DVHP6HMQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_AS.AppleDaily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=96725d7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201211/EQ2BGJLIPFAKJMSQA7DVHP6HMQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_AS.AppleDaily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"05814289a2cc7abcaa3176e91692c834550242d8","tid":2321881,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T01:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T-d0iedStyDAo0QfQATUwWkvnCg=/510x285/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TXTGG6N7KZBWLLSQB7GLU3PUIQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT-d0iedStyDAo0QfQATUwWkvnCg%3D%